## 🎮 Setup

1. Remove all **Crumbling Cookies** and **Milk Splashes** from the deck.
2. Deal **7 cards** to each player. Then deal **1 Milk Splash** to each player *(8 cards total per player)*.
3. Shuffle the Crumbling Cookies back in — **one fewer than the number of players**.
   - 2 players → 1 cookie · 3 players → 2 cookies
   - You may have leftover Milk Splashes — shuffle up to **2 extras** back into the deck.
4. Shuffle the deck.
5. **Whoever most recently ate something sweet goes first.**

---

## 🔄 On Your Turn

1. *(Optional)* Play any number of action cards from your hand.
2. **Draw a card** from the top of the deck.

> ⚠️ **Drew a Crumbling Cookie?**
> Play a **Milk Splash** to survive — then secretly reinsert the cookie anywhere in the deck. No Milk Splash? You're **eliminated**.
> Keep Milk Splashes in a separate discard pile, slightly spread out so players can count how many are there.

---

## 🏆 Winning

The **last player standing** wins the cookie jar. Glory, crumbs, and bragging rights are yours.

---

## 🃏 Card Reference

---

### 🐸 Leaping Frog — Defense
**Skip your draw phase.** Pass the turn to the next player — no draw, no risk.

If forced to draw multiple cards by another player's effect, each Leaping Frog skips **one** of those draws. *(Not valid for self-inflicted multi-draws.)*

*"Ribbit. Not today."*

---

### 🛡️ Shield Spell — Defense / Reaction
**Play as a reaction when any card is played** — including another Shield Spell. Cancel its effect entirely.

- Can be played **outside your turn** to protect another player.
- Two Shield Spells cancel **each other**.

*"Spell slot: used."*

---

### 🥣 Stir the Batter — Deck / Utility
**Shuffle the entire draw pile** in any order you choose. Place the deck face-down when done.

*"The prophecy has been... amended."*

---

### 🍄 Magic Mushroom — Info
**Look at the top 3 cards of the deck, (and replace them in any order?).**

*"It's giving… oracle energy."*

---

### 🎵 Vinyl Scratch — Disruption
**Reverse the turn order.** Play continues in the opposite direction for the rest of the game, or until another Vinyl Scratch is played.

*"B-side activated."*

---

### 🎲 Roll 4 Initiative — Dice
Roll the die and consult the result:

| Roll | Effect |
|------|--------|
| 1–3 | Skip your draw phase entirely |
| 4 | Draw up to 3 cards yourself *(must leave at least 1 in deck)* |
| 5–6 | Force any one player to draw up to 2 cards *(must leave at least 1 in deck)*|


*"Nat 4 goes hard actually."*

---

### 💀 Cursed Dice — Dice / Attack
**Play on any other player.** They must roll the die:

| Roll | Effect |
|------|--------|
| 1–2 | They discard 1 card of their choice |
| 3–4 | They discard 2 cards of their choice |
| 5–6 | They discard 3 cards of their choice |

*"The cookie crumbles… for thee."*

---

### 🍪 Tracking Cookies — Info
**Choose any player.** Peek at **3 random cards** from their hand *(or their full hand if they have fewer than 3)*.

*"Privacy settings: off."*

---

### 📜 Extra Serving — Draw
**Draw 2 cards** from the top of the deck. This **replaces** your normal end-of-turn draw.

*"Seconds? Don't mind if I do."*

---

### 🥛 Stolen Sip — Attack
**Point to a specific card in any player's hand** *(by position, not by name)*. They must reveal it. If it's a **Milk Splash**, they must give it to you. If it's anything else, nothing happens.

*"Oops. Their safety net: gone."*

---

### 📖 Mimicry Scroll — Wildcard
**Copy the effect of any card in the discard pile.** You may not copy Crumbling Cookie or Milk Splash.

*"I'm not plagiarizing. I'm paying homage."*

